rajawali.scenegraph

Interface IGraphNodeMember

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AAnimationObject3D, ALight, ATransformable3D, Camera, Camera2D, ChaseCamera, Cube, DirectionalLight, Line3D, NPrism, Object3D, OrthographicCamera, Plane, PointLight, PointSprite, ScreenQuad, SkeletalAnimationChildObject3D, SkeletalAnimationObject3D, Sphere, SpotLight, SquareTerrain, Terrain, VertexAnimationObject3D

    public interface IGraphNodeMember
    Generic interface which any member of IGraphNode must implement in order to be a part of the graph.
    Author:
    Jared Woolston (jwoolston@tenkiv.com)
